#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:35
#: of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"An ndarray is returned with one :class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` per column "
"when ``subplots=True``.      See Also     --------     "
"DataFrame.plot.barh : Horizontal bar plot.     DataFrame.plot : Make "
"plots of a DataFrame.     matplotlib.pyplot.bar : Make a bar plot with "
"matplotlib.      Examples     --------     Basic plot.      .. plot::"
"         :context: close-figs          >>> import maxframe.tensor as mt"
"         >>> import maxframe.dataframe as md         >>> df = "
"md.DataFrame({'lab':['A', 'B', 'C'], 'val':[10, 30, 20]})         >>> ax "
"= df.plot.bar(x='lab', y='val', rot=0)      Plot a whole dataframe to a "
"bar plot. Each column is assigned a     distinct color, and each row is "
"nested in a group along the     horizontal axis.      .. plot::         "
":context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, 40, 48, 52, 69, 88]"
"         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]         >>> index = "
"['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          'rabbit', 'giraffe', "
"'coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'speed': speed,"
"         ...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, index=index)"
"         >>> ax = df.plot.bar(rot=0)      Plot stacked bar charts for the"
" DataFrame      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> ax = "
"df.plot.bar(stacked=True)      Instead of nesting, the figure can be "
"split by column with     ``subplots=True``. In this case, a "
":class:`numpy.ndarray` of     :class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` are returned."
"      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> axes = "
"df.plot.bar(rot=0, subplots=True)         >>> axes[1].legend(loc=2)  # "
"doctest: +SKIP      If you don't like the default colours, you can "
"specify how you'd     like each column to be colored.      .. plot::"
"         :context: close-figs          >>> axes = df.plot.bar(         "
"...     rot=0, subplots=True, color={\"speed\": \"red\", \"lifespan\": "
"\"green\"}         ... )         >>> axes[1].legend(loc=2)  # doctest: "
"+SKIP      Plot a single column.      .. plot::         :context: close-"
"figs          >>> ax = df.plot.bar(y='speed', rot=0)      Plot only "
"selected categories for the DataFrame.      .. plot::         :context: "
"close-figs          >>> ax = df.plot.bar(x='lifespan', rot=0)"
msgstr ""
"当 ``subplots=True`` 时，返回一个包含每个列对应一个 :class:`matplotlib."
"axes.Axes` 的 ndarray。      参见     --------     DataFrame.plot.barh : "
"水平条形图。     DataFrame.plot : 绘制 DataFrame 图形。     matplotlib."
"pyplot.bar : 使用 matplotlib 绘制条形图。      示例     --------     基本"
"绘图。      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> import "
"maxframe.tensor as mt         >>> import maxframe.dataframe as md        "
" >>> df = md.DataFrame({'lab':['A', 'B', 'C'], 'val':[10, 30, 20]})      "
"   >>> ax = df.plot.bar(x='lab', y='val', rot=0)      将整个 DataFrame "
"绘制成条形图。每列分配一个独特的颜色，每行嵌套在水平轴的一个组中。      "
".. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> speed = [0.1, 17.5, "
"40, 48, 52, 69, 88]         >>> lifespan = [2, 8, 70, 1.5, 25, 12, 28]   "
"      >>> index = ['snail', 'pig', 'elephant',         ...          '"
"rabbit', 'giraffe', 'coyote', 'horse']         >>> df = md.DataFrame({'"
"speed': speed,         ...                    'lifespan': lifespan}, "
"index=index)         >>> ax = df.plot.bar(rot=0)      绘制 DataFrame 的"
"堆叠条形图      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> ax = "
"df.plot.bar(stacked=True)      可以通过 ``subplots=True`` 按列分割图形，"
"而不是嵌套。在这种情况下，返回一个 :class:`numpy.ndarray` 的 :class:`"
"matplotlib.axes.Axes`。      .. plot::         :context: close-figs      "
"    >>> axes = df.plot.bar(rot=0, subplots=True)         >>> axes[1]."
"legend(loc=2)  # doctest: +SKIP      如果不喜欢默认颜色，可以指定每列的"
"颜色。      .. plot::         :context: close-figs          >>> axes = df"
".plot.bar(         ...     rot=0, subplots=True, color={\"speed\": \"red"
"\", \"lifespan\": \"green\"}         ... )         >>> axes[1].legend(loc"
"=2)  # doctest: +SKIP      绘制单列。      .. plot::         :context: "
"close-figs          >>> ax = df.plot.bar(y='speed', rot=0)      仅绘制 "
"DataFrame 的选定类别。      .. plot::         :context: close-figs       "
"   >>> ax = df.plot.bar(x='lifespan', rot=0)"

